{"tid":55550,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一樣細個有陰影到大個唔鍾意嘅野/事","createTime":"2016-12-26T13:19:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T10:39:12.000Z","uid":5190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cefaec4fe03ca94ff3f4baad90d9fd40e6cf4ae3","tid":55550,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:19:27.000Z","msg":"細細個學游水 本身都好地地<br />\n直到有一次 個教練帶我去深水個邊學 屌佢老母一出去我就浸撚親 個陣仲要得4 5歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就無再開過游水 暑假都唔會去游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a594dc40ee2c59375a96708a64e775f2a65d582","tid":55550,"uid":49833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:36:17.000Z","msg":"都係關學游水事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企人話食魚皮就會識游水<br />\n我就成條魚嘅魚皮啪落口<br />\n食左一排 班大人就以為我鐘意食魚皮 次撚次都起魚皮俾我食<br />\n冇學過又點識游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家跌落水都識浮上面嘅<br />\n但魚皮我係點都唔會擺入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"473a22111042870f0b27a5ad418b3389e2a099e7","tid":55550,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:52:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細細個學游水 本身都好地地<br />\n直到有一次 個教練帶我去深水個邊學 屌佢老母一出去我就浸撚親 個陣仲要得4 5歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就無再開過游水 暑假都唔會去游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都類似係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c40ebc61f7c428830c8740228d11613b844eb73","tid":55550,"uid":29438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:59:13.000Z","msg":"細個曳鳩<br />\n有一次用蠟筆畫花同學隻手<br />\n個老師嬲到去拎把菜刀出黎扮斬我<br />\n果陣仲係未上幼稚園果d濕鳩班<br />\n所以一直對老師都好反感好淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a643bb4aa2dd30f888ab81a2089d8bee601878f1","tid":55550,"uid":63555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:16:43.000Z","msg":"細個小學三四年班去學游水<br />\n點知俾同期學游水嘅肥仔非禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個唔知咩叫非禮 一直無講出聲<br />\n但始終個次之後唔敢游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ad13679cef6222f79d224152d4752cdeff2b24","tid":55550,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:18:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細細個學游水 本身都好地地<br />\n直到有一次 個教練帶我去深水個邊學 屌佢老母一出去我就浸撚親 個陣仲要得4 5歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就無再開過游水 暑假都唔會去游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nME 2 <br />\n同你差唔多,但我係同呀媽仲有姨媽一家去,畀姨媽掉落泳池<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c820f107ee8ea7a5d466d128662ec4915b9e75","tid":55550,"uid":21924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:19:08.000Z","msg":"游水都幾多陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc46f789cb9f535b08230dd19d1c99ab55a8d32","tid":55550,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:26:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個小學三四年班去學游水<br />\n點知俾同期學游水嘅肥仔非禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個唔知咩叫非禮 一直無講出聲<br />\n但始終個次之後唔敢游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1483c5c4724f23a6ef3b47ae24490df3888acd76","tid":55550,"uid":63555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T14:49:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細個小學三四年班去學游水<br />\n點知俾同期學游水嘅肥仔非禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個唔知咩叫非禮 一直無講出聲<br />\n但始終個次之後唔敢游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg